
PRE-REQUIRES:
steam-runtime for compiling: http://media.steampowered.com/client/runtime/steam-runtime-sdk_latest.tar.xz
sudo apt-get install g++-multilib gcc-multilib

1) Run a terminal and type ./compile.sh
2) Place .vdf and .so files inside addons folder
3) Restart server (or use plugin_load addons/sample_plugin) and profit.
